n\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">collect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Collectors</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">toList</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>이 후 데이터를 출력하여 문제를 마무리 하였습니다!</p>\n<p>저는 그럼 즐거운 휴가를 보내도록 하겠습니다~ 감사합니다</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"12th Algorithm Study Memoirs","date":"2022년 10월 01일","description":"12번째 알고리즘 스터디 회고록입니다."}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/algorithm-study-memoir/11th_algorithm_study_memoir/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"11th Algorithm Study Memoirs"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/pycon_2022/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"PYCON 2022 에 참여하다"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"09ffa790-13ff-5c9f-9302-93ad5c98be1c","previousPostId":"b6562c16-11f7-53d7-a15e-6e4fc6040c09","nextPostId":"b598b303-472e-534f-a113-af08caeeaa2b"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383","3257411868"]}